  <title>Xanthomonas maltophilia infection presenting as erythematous nodules</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=4bb25a27666e08b9793e6b54eadf5409&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
